  (For ex: for_window [class="URxvt"] border none ) and comment that part out and restart i3, The border of urxvt doesnt re-appear. Is it a bug or is it by design? Any workaround this?&lt;/p&gt;
</title><link>https://faq.i3wm.org/question/6363/change-in-border-conf-not-updating/?comment=6364#comment-6364</link><description>This is by design. If you want it to reappear, just execute

    i3-msg "[class=URxvt] border normal"

 once.</description><pubDate>Thu, 30 Jul 2015 09:56:27 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://faq.i3wm.org/question/6363/change-in-border-conf-not-updating/?comment=6364#comment-6364</guid></item></channel></rss>